06:04.605 --> 06:05.605
Yeah, I was transferred--

06:05.685 --> 06:06.925
No, I don't care.

06:07.205 --> 06:10.165
Presumably in your old round, you put
things through the door, didn't you?

06:10.325 --> 06:11.845
Mate, there's no need to get lairy.

06:11.925 --> 06:14.005
